1. Creating the Helm chart file
2. Creating the Helm values file
3. Creating the template files
4. Packaging the Helm chart file
 
The file Chart.yaml describes the Helm chart on a high-level. 
Mandatory attributes include the chart's API version, the name, and the version.


The file values.yaml defines key-value pairs to be used to replace placeholders in the YAML template files. 


$ helm package .

Successfully packaged chart and saved it to: /root/web-app-2.5.4.tgz
The file web-app-2.5.4.tgz should exist in the current directory:

$ ls web-app-2.5.4.tgz

web-app-2.5.4.tgz